# Plan: Fix Greenblocks Hero Section Layout

## Overview

The hero section needs to be changed from a side-by-side grid layout to a full-width background image layout where the text overlays the image. Key differences identified:

### Current Issues (Image 1)
- Side-by-side grid layout with image confined to right column
- Image has rounded corners and is separate from the background
- Button has dark green fill (solid background)
- Brand name and byline on separate lines, small
- Title is too large/bold
- No gradient overlay for text readability

### Target Design (Image 2)
- Full-width hero image as background, extending edge-to-edge
- Text content overlaid on left side of the image
- Gradient overlay on left side for text readability
- Button is outline style (transparent with border)
- "Greenblocks by Aunova" on single line, larger
- Title is serif-style, lighter weight, more elegant
- Floating icons positioned within the image area (right side)

