### Task 2: Update Hero CSS for full-width background image
**File**: `src/pages/greenblocks.astro`

**Replace** all hero-related CSS with the new background-image layout:

```css
/* Hero Section - Full width background image */
.gb-hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Background image container */
.gb-hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
}

.gb-hero-bg-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center right;
}

/* Text overlay with gradient */
.gb-hero-overlay {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 6rem 0;
  /* Gradient overlay for text readability */
  background: linear-gradient(
    to right,
    rgba(245, 241, 235, 0.95) 0%,
    rgba(245, 241, 235, 0.85) 35%,
    rgba(245, 241, 235, 0.4) 60%,
    transparent 80%
  );
}

.gb-hero-content {
  max-width: 550px;
  padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
}

/* Brand styling */
.gb-hero-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.gb-brand-name {
  font-family: var(--gb-font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gb-text-primary);
}

.gb-brand-byline {
  font-family: var(--gb-font-body);
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--gb-text-muted);
}

.gb-hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--gb-text-muted);
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}

/* Hero title - smaller, lighter weight */
.gb-hero-title {
  font-family: var(--gb-font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.25;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--gb-text-primary);
}

.gb-hero-description {
  font-size: clamp(0.9375rem, 1.5vw, 1.0625rem);
  color: var(--gb-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

/* Floating icons - positioned on the right side of image */
.gb-hero-icons {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 3;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.gb-hero-icon {
  position: absolute;
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  border-radius: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: var(--gb-accent);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.gb-hero-icon-1 { top: 25%; right: 15%; }
.gb-hero-icon-2 { top: 45%; right: 8%; }
.gb-hero-icon-3 { top: 65%; right: 18%; }
```

