### Task 4: Update mobile responsive styles for hero
**File**: `src/pages/greenblocks.astro`

**Add/Update** responsive rules:

```css
@media (max-width: 1023px) {
  .gb-hero {
    min-height: auto;
  }

  .gb-hero-bg-image {
    object-position: center center;
  }

  .gb-hero-overlay {
    min-height: auto;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(245, 241, 235, 0.95) 0%,
      rgba(245, 241, 235, 0.8) 70%,
      transparent 100%
    );
  }

  .gb-hero-content {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .gb-hero-icons {
    display: none;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .gb-hero-overlay {
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .gb-hero-brand {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .gb-hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 2rem);
  }

  .gb-btn-outline {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
  }
}
```

