## Summary of Visual Changes

| Element | Current | Target |
|---------|---------|--------|
| **Layout** | Side-by-side grid | Full-width background image |
| **Image** | Rounded corners, right column | Edge-to-edge, behind content |
| **Overlay** | None | Left-to-right gradient for text readability |
| **Brand** | Stacked, small | Inline "Greenblocks by Aunova", larger |
| **Subtitle** | Green accent color | Muted gray |
| **Title** | Large, bold | Smaller, lighter weight |
| **Button** | Solid dark green fill | Outline style (transparent with border) |
| **Icons** | Hidden on mobile | Positioned on right side of image |

